---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Offerings | Chaos With Clarity" description="Three ways to work with Abby — Soul + Strategy, Chaos Circles, and Letters from Chaos.">

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <div style="background: var(--bg-alt); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 9rem; padding-bottom: 4.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width: 72rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem;">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Work Together</p>
      <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.5rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 0.9;">
        Offerings
      </h1>
      <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 1.25rem;">
        Three ways to work with Abby.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- 01 · SOUL + STRATEGY -->
  <div style="max-width: 72rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 2rem;">

    <!-- Section number header -->
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3.5rem;">
      <span style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 3.5rem; color: var(--border); line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 700;">01</span>
      <div style="height: 1px; flex: 1; background: var(--border);"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="soul-grid reveal">

      <!-- Left: info -->
      <div>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 2.25rem; color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Soul + Strategy</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2.25rem;">For founders &amp; professionals</p>
        <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
          You've built something real. The numbers are there — or close enough. But something inside is off. This isn't coaching. This isn't therapy. It's a mirror.
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0 0 3rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.9rem;">
          {['Runway + pricing clarity', 'Emotional patterns blocking growth', 'Lifestyle design that actually fits you', 'One-on-one, held with full presence'].map(item => (
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text);">
              <span style="color: var(--sage); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1em;">—</span>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="https://calendly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-fill">Book a Call</a>
        <p style="color: var(--dim); font-size: 0.7rem; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.75rem;">Replace with your Calendly link</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: price panel -->
      <div style="background: var(--bg-alt); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 3rem 2.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.75rem; align-self: start;">
        <p class="eyebrow">Investment</p>
        <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(3rem, 5.5vw, 4.75rem); color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-weight: 700;">₹15,000</p>
        <div style="height: 1px; background: var(--border);"></div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--muted);">90 minutes, one on one</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--muted);">Held with full presence</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--muted);">No scripts. Just truth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div style="max-width: 72rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem;">
    <div style="height: 1px; background: var(--border);"></div>
  </div>


  <!-- 02 + 03 -->
  <div style="max-width: 72rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 2rem;">
    <div class="pair-grid" style="border: 1px solid var(--border);">

      <!-- Chaos Circles -->
      <div class="pair-left reveal" style="padding: 3rem; border-right: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <span style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--border); line-height: 1; display: block; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 700;">02</span>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.75rem; color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.35rem;">Chaos Circles</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">6 people · 6 weeks</p>
        <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 2.25rem; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; font-weight: 600;">₹8,000</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;">per person</p>
        <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          Six people who are done pretending everything is fine. Six weeks of poems, questions, and the kind of honesty that only happens in small rooms.
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0 0 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem;">
          {['Weekly poems + guided reflection', 'Money & soul conversations', 'Intimate small group', 'A container for real things'].map(item => (
            <li style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;">
              <span style="color: var(--sage); flex-shrink: 0;">—</span>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          Next circle: <span style="color: var(--text); font-weight: 400;">March 2026</span>
        </p>
        <a href="https://typeform.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline">Join Waitlist</a>
        <p style="color: var(--dim); font-size: 0.7rem; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.75rem;">Replace with your Typeform link</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Letters from Chaos -->
      <div class="reveal" style="padding: 3rem;">
        <span style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--border); line-height: 1; display: block; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 700;">03</span>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.75rem; color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.35rem;">Letters from Chaos</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Curated poems · digital download</p>
        <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 2.25rem; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; font-weight: 600;">₹999</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;">one-time</p>
        <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          A curated collection of poems from three years of writing — on money, mortality, love, and the strange gift of being alive.
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0 0 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem;">
          {['30+ pages of poetry', 'My personal reflections on each poem', 'Designed for slow, repeated reading', 'Your pocket poet for uncertain days'].map(item => (
            <li style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;">
              <span style="color: var(--dim); flex-shrink: 0;">—</span>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="https://buy.stripe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-ghost">Buy Now</a>
        <p style="color: var(--dim); font-size: 0.7rem; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.75rem;">Replace with your Stripe link</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div style="max-width: 72rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem;">
    <div style="height: 1px; background: var(--border);"></div>
  </div>


  <!-- TESTIMONIAL + CTA -->
  <div class="reveal" style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 2rem 7rem; text-align: center;">
    <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      "Abby's poems land like quiet thunder."
    </p>
    <cite style="font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); font-style: normal;">— A reader</cite>
    <div style="margin-top: 3.5rem;">
      <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 1.75rem;">Not sure which is right for you?</p>
      <a href="/about" class="btn btn-ghost">Read About Abby →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .soul-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .pair-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .soul-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .pair-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pair-left { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border) !important; }
  }
</style>
